// Small Todo App - Angular - Node.js
/**
 * Features:
 * 1. Todo Interface will show Add Task, Edit Task, Update Task, Delete Task in Angular
 * 2. Addding task --> it will add it in the Db and fetch form the db.
 * 3. Editing todo --> it will fetch the particular task with an Id and then It will be shown it.
 * 4. Updating todo --> it will take an data from an User then find the Id then update the particular Id
 * 5. Delete todo --> it will take an Id from user it will findout and then delete the todo
 */

 Technologies are going to use in this 
 1. Angular - Frontend
 2. Node.js - Backend
 3. Express - Backend
 4. Mongodb - Database
 5. Mongoose - Connection

